{"type": "article", "id": 59723, "title": "作为建筑材料的沙子，还能做成咖啡杯？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-12-26T23:10:04Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 55451, "name": "HARAC"}, {"id": 55452, "name": "AIAIAI"}, {"id": 24002, "name": "Front"}, {"id": 55453, "name": "Sulapac ®"}, {"id": 55454, "name": "The Foundry"}, {"id": 55455, "name": "Sofia Lagerkvist"}, {"id": 55456, "name": "Anna Lindgren"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 119, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181226215738tvojGZ97HLa63BDW.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #545454; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #545454} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Ramel by The Foundry</h3><p>受到不断变化的沙丘的启发， The Foundry 开发出一种将沙粒转化为可塑造介质的材料 Ramel，可以转化成各种功能性或是美学产品，比如这款向全球化文化致敬的咖啡杯。</p><p>以实验探索为核心，设计师从迪拜当地的环境中汲取灵感，创造了这款沙质咖啡杯，整个团队研究了阿联酋丰富的沙石资源，目标是将沙子用于可再生产品。</p><p>设计师创造一种复合材料，将沙子的视觉、触觉和隔热性能与陶瓷的可铸性相结合，造型也很别致。售价 1220 元，<a href=\"https://thefoundry.ltd/products/ramel-c01\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812262158438soLAV7tQfeS9Hq4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812262158442QSPwiVUkuZsb1mr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215846OplCsx3jEbv97YfG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215846a3rcBOnkDNYgsCJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sulapac ® by Suvi Haimi &amp; Lauraky Llönen</h3><p>2018 年 10 月，欧洲议会通过了法令，开列了一份一次性塑料产品的禁用清单，同时还开列了一批应减产但尚不完全禁止的塑料产品的清单。</p><p>以消费者能够负担得起的价格大批量生产令人信服的塑料替代品，能够做到这一点的企业前途将无限光明。若干芬兰公司正在跃跃欲试。其中最著名的一家是 Sulapac ®，也就是同名创新包装材料的生产企业。</p><p>“与塑料相比，Sulapac 最大的优势在于 100%可生物降解且不含微塑料。”公司 CEO 兼联合创始人之一 Suvi Haimi 表示，“Sulapac 的性能优于其他可持续替代产品的方面是生物降解速度、二氧化碳足迹、阻隔性能以及独特的外观。”</p><p>比如这套 Sulapac 制作的化妆品容器，是用不含塑料、基于木材、可生物降解的材料制造的，生产商可以用现有机器设备进行加工。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215925NIGXa2AClvLJucZp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668116\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215925pbiS7RmfoaNZQUxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215926aYP0Qh5kArg3ByKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215927jOec1L8Am9R4NdxS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215928c679uXwsTCS308lz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562092\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018122621592868mZTKaErpWLF0eU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226215929qjkdhAOx9LMPwGo5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617813\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.sulapac.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sulapac</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Loop Chairs by Sofia Lagerkvist &amp; Anna Lindgren for Front</h3><p>瑞典设计团队 Front 的两位设计师 Sofia Lagerkvist 和 Anna Lindgren 设计了这把名为 Loop 的椅子。</p><p>这是一把有扶手的优雅的可堆叠椅子，主题是一系列的可变截面曲线，它可能是一组令人感到困惑的笔画，设计师把椅子放在一个全新的想象世界中。售价 450 美元，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/shop/design/loop-chair-by-front-qeeboo-05-12-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220138kg1NdyTG0vl9esqA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220139HaqEyhiZRcm9btLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220140doPEMm5phRCXz2fB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220140EiR2PpCyKSo7GcZx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220141OIenSzxRw7YTBqFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220142fSOZbAaVem1joHu2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812262201437iVHXpTEtuQJ6MoN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pipe &amp; Tracks 2.0 by AIAIAI</h3><p>说到丹麦耳机品牌 AIAIAI，也许大家会感到陌生，然而它却是丹麦国宝级别的耳机品牌，总部位于哥本哈根，长期致力于发展设计高品质的音响产品的音频设备。以简约个性的设计，上乘的做工以及专业级音质，在世界各地取得了非常好的反响。Pipes 和 Tracks 2.0 是 AIAIAI 推出的最新设计，相较于 1.0 版本更加年轻，且能匹配任何 Google 设备。</p><p>Tracks 2.0 作为中端耳机市场的竞争者，提供了入耳式耳机的替代方案，没有耳罩的耳机的体积和重量相对都要小一些，使其成为旅行、跑步或通勤的绝佳选择。售价 60 美元，<a href=\"https://aiaiai.dk/headphones/tracks/black\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220420hzt3ksfVFd4b2KUS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220421x9Iz4mFf3kWycdow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220421SQ97woBGame6hc2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220422oamhUQwR9Ikrpe76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220423HAwiyVs25TQkIO6z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220423w0j2HNrqhzQGCmxJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220424n0FX5CPGjRwi4o1J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220424ZBpF5wzC034LW7Oi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Line Paper Cutter by HARAC</h3><p>你有看过鼠标造型的纸张裁切刀吗？这款名为 HARAC 的纸裁切刀掌握在你手中，顺畅的弯曲度，流利的切割体验，好像在纸上跳舞一般，无论是裁纸还是做剪报都能很优雅，让裁纸成为一种趣味。</p><p>压下按钮陶瓷切刀即可裁切纸张，使用方法简便，各个年龄层的用户都能使用。自转式刀刃设计，各种形状及曲线都可以完美裁切。售价 14.94 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0037W57LK/?tag=yankodesign05-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220522hGJf1bukLozYFPl8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220524tsC5mfQSy06akJ7z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220524kFQrK6nCymGwoPMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201812262205254mJUt1g5kcWOvTQ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181226220525nI7oOuYNqiSyX9gB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}